        "title": "Removing the &quot;Show All&quot; category from the portfolio gallery with filtering category",
        "body": "<p>I'm currently working on a portfolio gallery in one template.<\/p>\n<p>I have Portfolio Gallery with filtering category\nI want to remove the whole category &quot;Show All&quot; and set another one first.\nI tried this code but it only removes the button.<\/p>\n<pre><code>.button-group .button[data-filter=&quot;*&quot;] {\ndisplay: none;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>}<\/p>\n<p>How can I do this?<\/p>\n<p>I appreciate the answers<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https://codepen.io/ValentinaY/project/editor/DvWkvy#\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">portfolio gallery<\/a><\/p>\n",
