        "creation_date": 1613650085,
        "body": "<p>I make it.<\/p>\n<p>1.Rename<\/p>\n<pre><code>&lt;a class=&quot;button is-checked&quot; data-filter=&quot;*&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Show all&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>with<\/p>\n<pre><code>&lt;a class=&quot;button is-checked&quot; data-filter=&quot;.klinkers&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;KLINKERS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>2.I add filter in<\/p>\n<pre><code>/* Filter - Isotope */\nvar $grid = $('.grid').isotope({\n    // options\n    itemSelector: '.element-item',\n    layoutMode: 'fitRows',\n    filter: '.klinkers'\n});\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>---&gt; filter: '.klinkers'<\/p>\n",
